@PROCESSES
demo-render: Root.tsx <Composition> → remotion studio preview → remotion render <id> → mp4
ep01-production: 93 scenes via Sequence + TransitionSeries → 38160 frames @ 30fps → ~21 min
ep01-structure: Intro overlay → Myth 1..10 × (ChapterCard + PRO/CON SideList + ExplainerSlide + evidence screenshots + MythBustedCard closure) → Outro

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: components/** | templates/** | styles/tokens | hooks/**
external: remotion (AbsoluteFill, Sequence, interpolate, spring, useCurrentFrame), @remotion/transitions

@STANDARDS
- All wrapped in PrautVideoFrame (ShortVideoDemo → PrautShortFrame)
- Default episodeNumber "00" for showcases, numbered for production
- 1920×1080 @ 30fps (ShortVideo: 1080×1920)
- Demo data in Czech (diacritics require latin-ext subset)

@EP01_LOCAL_HELPERS
SideList: one-side list with › bullets, purple[200] heading, inline spring opacity
ScreenPlaceholder: BrowserMockup placeholder for evidence
DefOverlay: small top-center tooltip, 15% H-padding, no bg darkening
KeyPoints: ordered list of key takeaways
BigQuote: gradient large-quote callout
MythBustedCard: closure card — italic myth + verdict

@EP01_PATTERNS (established best practices)
- No watermark (PrautVideoFrame includeWatermark=false default)
- WebcamPlaceholder 240×240 green-screen (#00FF00), bottom-RIGHT, no border
- ChapterCard prefix="MÝTUS" (overrides "KAPITOLA")
- IntroAnimation: logo 640×640, no tagline, gap=240, paddingBottom=240
- SideList › bullets (not checkmarks), purple[200] heading, inline spring opacity
- DefOverlay top-center, no darkening, ≤ 70% width
- All local helpers (SideList, DefOverlay, KeyPoints, BigQuote, MythBustedCard) have enter+exit+hierarchy animations
